c3r pause [TARGET_REPO]

Pauses all agents cooperatively: writes a PAUSED flag in each worktree's
.c3r/ dir. Agents check this flag between iterations and spin-sleep rather
than starting a new iteration. Any in-flight iteration (including a running
training job) is allowed to finish first — nothing is killed.

Also updates state.json ("paused": true) and redraws the status board.

Resume with `c3r resume`.
