c3r reset [TARGET_REPO] AGENT_NAME

DESTRUCTIVE. Removes an agent completely:
  1. Confirms with y/N prompt.
  2. Removes the git worktree (<parent>/<repo>-<name>)
  3. Deletes the branch (agent/<name>)
  4. Removes the agent entry from state.json
  5. Archives the Discord thread (doesn't delete it — history is preserved)
