  - tmux, flock, python3, git, claude CLI are all on PATH
  - claude CLI is logged in (claude --version)
  - Discord bot can post in the configured channel
  - Discord bot can create threads (permission check)
  - If a target is given: state.json is valid, worktrees exist

Exits 0 if everything is fine, non-zero otherwise.
