Symlinks $C3R_DIR/c3r into ~/.local/bin/c3r so the command is on PATH.
Creates ~/.local/bin if missing. If ~/.local/bin is not on your PATH, prints
the line to add to your shell rc.

After install, `c3r` is available from any directory.
